    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>One Room Dungeon</strong> 中，扮演一位可爱的地下城守护者，开启你的冒险之旅。这是一款结合了类Roguelike团队构筑与策略性背包管理的游戏。你的小小单间地下城就是你的堡垒——巧妙地布置手下、奇妙的遗物和有趣的道具，击退那些来侵扰的冒险者吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.poster.avif?t=1745939266\" width=320 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.webm?t=1745939266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/401c38ab37a722b65c4a95cc36d107f3.mp4?t=1745939266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>格子式背包管理</strong><br>使用格子系统精确地整理地下城内的物品。每样物品都有它的位置，保持整洁和合理规划是制胜关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.poster.avif?t=1745939266\" width=640 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.webm?t=1745939266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/5abb5b113a07bc94259ca1ab98e7ad6e.mp4?t=1745939266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单位与道具养成</strong><br>随着游戏进行，不断强化你的手下和魔法道具，让他们变得更强大，更有效地对抗来犯的敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>专属奥义技能</strong><br>每个单位都拥有独特的奥义技能，满足特定条件后即可发动，瞬间扭转战局。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.poster.avif?t=1745939266\" width=500 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.webm?t=1745939266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065810/extras/8262358059e207b68d9e765f105bbe5f.mp4?t=1745939266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随机事件与邂逅</strong><br>旅途中你会遇到有趣的朋友和商人，他们会向你出售稀有道具和强力装备。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遗物、装备与药水</strong><br>通过多种方式增强战斗能力，组合出属于你的策略和流派。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强大Boss挑战</strong><br>面对强敌Boss的试炼，你的策略与团队实力将接受真正的考验。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样的初始角色与开局构筑</strong><br>选择不同的初始角色与开局遗物，打造专属的战术风格，每一局都有全新的可能性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守护你的地下城（你的家），<strong>击败那些冒险者</strong>，成为最强的地下城守护者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One Room Dungeon</strong> 即将开启！</p>",
